history.content:
I'm worried about my chance of getting off the waitlist for cs 161 and cs 186.

If I don't get off the waitlist, I drop below the minimum number of units required for the semester (I'll be at 12 units only). But then I won't be able to enroll in any other class because the add/drop deadline will have passed already. I've already invested a considerable amount of time in both classes and did the first project for 186. 

I am also a senior and need these classes to graduate.
